===Etymology 1===
{{ja-kanjitab|とう|yomi=o}}
From {{der|ja|ltc|-|sort=とう}} {{m|zh|等|tr=tong<sup>X</sup>||step, grade}}, extended to mean ''... kind of thing''.

====Pronunciation====
{{ja-pron|とう|acc=1|acc_ref=DJR}}

====Adverb====
