# [[et cetera]]

====Suffix====
{{ja-pos|suffix|とう}}

# [[rank]], [[class]], [[order]]
# [[et cetera]], that [[kind]] of thing, [[and so on]]

=====Usage notes=====
* For the ''et cetera'' sense, the reading ''tō'' is somewhat more formal than ''nado''. Spelling the native Japanese readings of this character in hiragana (such as {{m|ja|など}} or {{m|ja|ら}}) is standard practice, as it prevents phonetic and tonal ambiguity with this formal Sino‐Japanese reading.

