===Etymology 4===
{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|ら}}
From {{inh|ja|ojp|-|sort=ら}}. Likely related to {{ja-r|-ろ}}.

====Pronunciation====
{{ja-pron|ら}}

====Suffix====
{{ja-pos|suffix|ら}}

# {{ng|[[pluralizer]]}}
#: {{syn|ja|{{ja-r|達|-たち}}|{{ja-r|共|-ども}}}}
#: {{ja-uxi|[[我]] → 我'''ら'''|われ → われ'''ら'''|I → '''we'''}}
#: {{ja-uxi|[[これ]] → これ'''ら'''|this → '''these'''}}
# {{ng|[[qualifier]], [[softener]]}}: [[around]], [[about]]
#: {{ja-uxi|[[今日]]'''等'''|きょう'''ら'''|roughly today}}
#: {{ja-uxi|[[そこ]]'''等'''[[辺]]|そこ'''ら''' へん|that area '''around''' there}}

=====Usage notes=====
* {{ja-uk|kana=hira|ら}}
* Spelling this suffix in hiragana visually distinguishes it from the kanji's formal Sino‐Japanese reading, {{ja-r|等|とう}}, which can also occupy the same grammatical position.
* Attached to words referring to people, the pluralizer may be slightly humbling or derogatory (though not to the extent of {{ja-r|共|-ども}}).

